metadata.name: Sunray #01
metadata.description:
Photographer: Saber Deilami
Year Taken: 2016

Here is my Genesis NFT.

(To my beautiful little sister, Sara; When you were with us, I didn't have any photography tools, and when I started photography, you weren't there. I wish you were, and I could make your beauty eternal. You joined mother nature, and now the beauty of nature reminds me of the beauty of you. I remember you with every beat of my heart. Rest in Peace).
